<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ART - Official website</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Official website for the Old Vic Production of ART written by Yasmina Reza, translated by Christopher Hampton"
    />
    <link
      href="https://unpkg.com/tailwindcss@^2/dist/tailwind.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="w-11\/12 md:w-1/2 mx-auto text-center">
    <header class="py-5">
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm">
        David Pugh & Dafydd Rogers present the Old Vic Production of <br />
        ART written by Yasmina Reza, translated by Christopher Hampton <br />
        originally directed by Matthew Warchus
      </p>
      <img src="/img/art-tt.svg" alt="ART" />
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class="quote">
        <blockquote class="font-black text-4xl">"A PHENOMENON"</blockquote>
        <cite>The Times</cite>
      </div>
      <div class="cast my-5">
        <p class="text-2xl">
          <span class="text-xl">Starring</span> <br />
          Nigel Havers, Denis Lawson and Stephen Tompkinson
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="video py-5">
        <iframe
          width="100%"
          height="550"
          class="border-4"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LzJGG0A6VSo"
          title="YouTube video player"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="content md:text-xl">
        <p>ART is one of the most successful comedies ever.</p>
        <p>
          ART is the winner of an Olivier, Tony, Moliere and every other major
          world theatre award.
        </p>
        <p>ART is a masterpiece.</p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="mt-36 px-5">
      <div class="form-area">
        <h3 class="uppercase font-black mb-4">Sign up to our newsletter</h3>
        <form
          action="https://www.createsend.com/t/subscribeerror?description="
          method="post"
          id="subForm"
          class="js-cm-form flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 justify-center"
          data-id="5B5E7037DA78A748374AD499497E309E4AA9E715F599425FCCD05FC368B669E0B1264A5C9086592B7A887AB2EAA0A08514E956923CAE1B241DD98594DA80761E"
          data-nordpass-autofill="identity"
          data-np-checked="1"
        >
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="sr-only" for="fieldName">Name</label>
            <input
              class="form-control px-4 py-4 md:mr-52 border-2 w-full"
              id="fieldName"
              name="cm-name"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Name..."
            />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="sr-only" for="fieldEmail">Email</label>
            <input
              class="
                form-control
                js-cm-email-input
                px-4
                py-4
                mr-52
                border-2
                w-full
              "
              id="fieldEmail"
              name="cm-uyikidr-uyikidr"
              type="email"
              required=""
              placeholder="Email..."
            />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="
                js-cm-submit-button
                px-4
                py-4
                md:mr-52
                border-2
                w-full
                bg-gray-200
              "
            >
              SUBMIT
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
        <script
          type="text/javascript"
          src="https://js.createsend1.com/javascript/copypastesubscribeformlogic.js"
        ></script>
      </div>
      <div class="credit text-xs my-10">
        a <a href="https://www.brackets.digital" target="_blank">{}</a> site
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
